lines.text: i lost myself on a cool damp night
gave myself in that misty light
was hypnotized by a strange delight
i made wine from the lilac tree
lost my heart in it's recipe
it make me see what i want to see
and be what i want to be
when i think more than i ought to think
i do things i never should do
i drink much more than i ought to drink
i feel unsteady like my love
i feel unsteady, where's my love?
